Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.61,0:24:27.57,Main03,SISTER/SHINPACHI,0,0,0,,The next episode...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.57,0:24:29.75,Main03,SISTER/SHINPACHI,0,0,0,,"Sometimes You Can't Tell\NJust By Meeting Someone."
